#. Tag: para
#: creatingproject.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new project can be created by pressing the <guibutton>New Project</"
"guibutton> button or selecting a <emphasis>project template</emphasis> in "
"the <link linkend=\"startup-view\">Startup View</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nov projekt lahko ustvarite tako, da pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Nov projekt</"
"guibutton> ali izberete <emphasis>predlogo projekta</emphasis> v <link "
"linkend=\"startup-view\">Pogledu ob zagonu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingproject.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will create a new project with default values defined in <xref linkend="
"\"configure-plan-dialog\" xrefstyle=\"select:title\"/> or from values "
"defined in the template. The Project Settings Dialog will open to enable you "
"to define project specific properties like <emphasis>project name</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>manager</emphasis> and <emphasis>target times</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"To bo ustvarilo nov projekt s privzetimi vrednostmi, določenimi v <xref "
"linkend=\"configure-plan-dialog\" xrefstyle=\"select:title\"/> ali iz "
"vrednosti, definiranih v predlogi. Odprlo se bo pogovorno okno z "
"nastavitvami projekta, v katerem boste lahko definirali lastnosti, "
"specifične za projekt, kot so <emphasis>ime projekta</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>voda</emphasis> in <emphasis>ciljni časi</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingproject.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you create your first project, consider creating resources in a "
"separate file. When you refer to this file in your project(s), you do not "
"need to define your resources again, and you can coordinate resource usage "
"across projects."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite svoj prvi projekt, razmislite o ustvarjanju virov v ločeni "
"datoteki. Ko se sklicujete na to datoteko v svojih projektih, vam ni treba "
"znova definirati virov in lahko uskladite uporabo virov med projekti."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingproject.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "See <xref linkend=\"managing-resources\" xrefstyle=\"select:title\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <xref linkend=\"managing-resources\" xrefstyle=\"select:title\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingproject.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To coordinate resource usage across projects you can use the &portfolio;."
msgstr ""
"Za usklajevanje uporabe virov med projekti lahko uporabite &portfolio;."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingproject.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "A useful structure could be something like this:"
msgstr "Uporabna struktura bi lahko bila nekaj takega:"

#. Tag: screen
#: creatingproject.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Resources\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- SharedResources.plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Taskmodules\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- Task modules (if any)\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Templates\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- Project templates (if any)\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Projects\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- &lt;project 1&gt;.plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- &lt;project 2&gt;.plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- etc"
msgstr ""
"Plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Resources\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- SharedResources.plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Taskmodules\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- Task modules (if any)\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Templates\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- Project templates (if any)\n"
"    &nbsp;!-- Projects\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- &lt;project 1&gt;.plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- &lt;project 2&gt;.plan\n"
"    &nbsp;!      !-- etc"
